      "descriptionModule": {
        "briefSummary": "ROSETTA STUDY: This study will evaluate the safety, tolerability, and efficacy of Rosnilimab in subjects with moderate to severe ulcerative colitis (UC)",
        "detailedDescription": "This is a Phase 2, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, parallel-group, multicenter study to evaluate the efficacy, safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics (PK), pharmacodynamics (PD), and immunogenicity of rosnilimab in subjects with moderate to severe ulcerative colitis (UC)."
      },
